name: Uocvueling
tagline: Open source flights company management web application.
body:
### Welcome to UOCVueling project.
This project aims to develope a web application to manage flight sites but in a fully free and open way. You are really encourage to participate! To do so just clone the repository and start collaborating:

```
git clone git://github.com/uocvueling/uocvueling.git
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
